{
  "texts": [
    "To generate a realistic visual from a semantic sketch that is provided as input, conditional GANs [75] can be utilized.",
    "Some examples of things includes, with the use of the given semantic information, photorealistic translations of a metropolis, residences, a real face, natural surroundings, and automobiles may be discovered.",
    "Text/Audio to image generationThe neural net can synthesize visuals autonomously from texts with GAN.",
    "TAC-GAN advented by Dash et al.",
    "in year 2017 synthesizes images from text descriptions."
  ]
}